Task: Understanding VPN working.

Tools: free Proton VPN, browser.

Procedure:
Step-1: Installed proton VPN from "https://protonvpn.com/download-windows"
Step-2: Connected VPN and checked whether the VPN is connected by checking the ip address from the Website "whatismyipaddress.com".
Step-3: Checked the Encryption used for the specific virtual server connected and doesnt even reflect the trace of wherebeing of the system location.
Step-4: Now disconnected the VPN and checked for the encryption, but found no encryption and the location of the system used as well was known.
Step-5: Checked ffor the VPN benefits offered within the settings option.

Observation:
- Helps to secure Network and be anonymous.
- Preventing data throttling as the data consumed cannot be detected as the location and the data usage will be encrypted.
- It helps to view the application which is banned within this country.


